2026-05-13T03:56:52.9835003Z 13    <!--
2026-05-13T03:56:52.9835580Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T03:56:52.9836706Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-13T03:56:52.9837920Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-13T03:56:52.9838842Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-13T03:56:52.9839835Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
